            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>超微電腦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SMCI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SMCI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SMCI-US</a>)截至台北時間20日21:30股價下跌8.43美元，報22.36美元，跌幅27.38%，成交量33,363,491（股），盤中最高價22.51美元、最低價22.36美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.27%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：-0.45%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：-0.28%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+0.87%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>超微電腦(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:SMCI:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/SMCI\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">SMCI-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.36%</li> <li>近 1 月：-4.26%</li> <li>近 3 月：-1.03%</li> <li>近 6 月：-32.79%</li> <li>今年以來：+5.19%</li></ul></section></main>",
